{"tid":494541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"測量師學會網站驚現無碼AV女！疑被入侵變鹹網","createTime":"2017-12-09T17:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T17:11:15.000Z","uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2896aff5f6a73758c07c495db787172aff3aacc","tid":494541,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171209/large/1512833805_81c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171209%2Flarge%2F1512833805_81c6.png&h=65a56831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n測量師學會的網站首頁，今日起突然出現兩張色情照片，涉及的性愛場面均完全無打格，無論是中文版還是英文版都不能倖免，但網站的其他頁面則暫時正常。<br />\n<br />\n記者在昨晚9時45分登入網站時，該兩張色情照片仍在頁面，惟記者昨晚11時半再查看時，網站已不能登入，相信已被暫停服務。測量師學會昨晚10時51分在facebook專頁表示，網站暫時要維修，為引起不便致歉，多謝大家忍耐（temporarily under maintenance. Thank you for your patience and sorry for the inconvenience caused.）。<br />\n會長何國鈞接受《蘋果》查詢時表示，已得悉相關事情，相信是被黑客攻擊所致，學會的技術人員正在維修，他也感到非常不解。被問到最近是否有得罪任何人，何國鈞笑指「真係唔知呀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171210/57562245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171210%2F57562245&d=BjJ2hMaJX7GUioK5eM7Dqf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=7e326ed8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171210%2F57562245&h=ebbf094d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171210/57562245</a><br />\n<br />\nIT狗又要俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213a30190481ee89ac0ba55c406ef15d6cb8422e","tid":494541,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來飛影出左唔好推<br />\n<br />\n測量師學會網站驚現無碼AV女！疑被入侵變鹹網<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/494507/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/494507/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}